txt.en: Gond Orchal has been corrupted by a gaunt-lord who is raising Wights from the various tombs. This evil must be defeated.
Mission: The Tombs of Gond Orchal
'Well done, [placeholder]! You have defeated the gaunt-lord!'
A gaunt-lord is corrupting Gond Orchal. Clear the tombs of Wights and defeat this evil.
Find and defeat the gaunt-lord corrupting Gond Orchal
